    "title": "Improve accessibility focus handling",
    "body": "<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_BEGIN -->\n## 変更点\n- 再描画後にキーボードフォーカスが失われないよう、追加・編集・保存・削除・完了切替後のフォーカス復元を追加\n- 画面全体の `aria-live` を専用のスクリーンリーダー向けステータス領域に置き換え、操作結果を通知\n- 入力欄へ移動するリンクで確実に対象へフォーカスし、フォーカスリングとタップ領域を強化\n\n## build通過\n- `npm run build` 通過\n\n## permissions不変\n- `public/manifest.json` は未変更\n- permissions は `['storage']` のまま\n<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_END -->\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents/bc-93502344-aae1-49f6-b4a6-2cf5153fe858\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" width=\"114\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-93502344-aae1-49f6-b4a6-2cf5153fe858\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" width=\"131\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;</div>\n\n",
